          <p>A bold first question, but in a space such as crypto, being skeptical is good. We hope to bring everything we plan to fruition and see no reason to abandon this project and become universally hated over what would mostl likely be a couple hundred dollars, and more importantly, we want to create an enviroment where donating isn't an awkward yearly tradition triggered by an email and a sense of guilt, but a low cost, low effort, fun way to give a little back each day.</p>
